{{Quote|May I present Lama Su, Prime Minister of Kamino.|[[Taun We/Legends|Taun We]] to [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]]|<ref name="Episode 2">{{Film|II}}</ref>}}
The position of '''Prime Minister''' was the political leader of [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]].

The Prime Minister was also the head of the ruling council of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] colony governors. It also had to deal with the offworlders.

In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], the Prime Minister of Kamino was [[Lama Su/Legends|Lama Su]].<ref name="Episode 2" />

